{"tid":1736202,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"預感今晚風向會開始分化入邊同學同救援手足","createTime":"2019-11-18T17:04:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T10:16:14.000Z","uid":208722,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"3fa4afbb22e18ea83e29f9a28150d6143bcc1e15","tid":1736202,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:04:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efc4480fd6717c0b3301e204d0ac2273d342e1a4","tid":1736202,"uid":338636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:07:51.000Z","msg":"[正能量撚]出去之前，希望你可以睇下呢個po<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1734559\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1734559</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d0e9d491b6360a09984add8eb5c1db2cf5c98d33","tid":1736202,"uid":108902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:08:56.000Z","msg":"Lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cee2e99fd8397797e0972ab997087625d880eff4","tid":1736202,"uid":20696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:09:53.000Z","msg":"不分化<br />\n我地係命運共同體，決策錯誤集體承擔，馬後炮於事無補，親者痛仇者快。今日陣亡咗好多個，但救手足係心甘情願，兩邊都係我地手足，係英雄。<br />\n投降嘅手足可以理解，佢地缺水缺糧精神崩潰心靈軟弱，仲要有傷在身，仲有唔少細路仔。"},{"pid":"f4b18a3157b74467d9daee957bfc66a70ac27a21","tid":1736202,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:10:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da55ffd14f17337c8b94fd74ef664076da1eadaf","tid":1736202,"uid":189157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:11:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a13e80044e4584efc811611f26396ea223c388e","tid":1736202,"uid":131122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:11:17.000Z","msg":"不分化"},{"pid":"0c0a1b839f8de73bcb423de2c799a347a2972aa2","tid":1736202,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:11:23.000Z","msg":"終於有人講"},{"pid":"0e9d76e45ad3c6ce8f0e2714dc1efb31f52a5bb1","tid":1736202,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:11:33.000Z","msg":"不分化"},{"pid":"b917d9626f2f1cf75692b5da03ff4c8b62753d3f","tid":1736202,"uid":130797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:12:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mikfukf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmikfukf.jpg&h=de8cf7f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d23847e7e9c5de516218741825039f88f607e36","tid":1736202,"uid":165682,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:13:53.000Z","msg":"不分化<br />\n不割蓆 <br />\n不篤灰<br />\n兄弟爬山<br />\n手足不是condom<br />\n和勇一家<br />\n前線決定<br />\n相信手足<br />\nBe water 不守點<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04a5d6d9ee32157796e334b76b6e60faad63be89","tid":1736202,"uid":66202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:15:37.000Z","msg":"啲五毛已經傾巢而出, 次次一完場就出晒嚟"},{"pid":"10551498a66765ab73226773ba67afde28c87300","tid":1736202,"uid":318612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:17:31.000Z","msg":"Sorry借一借位<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家成日都話手足唔係condom,<br />\n咁我地聽朝一齊去支持佢地</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gUHmpHa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgUHmpHa.jpg&h=8a668bc0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cd061696e2506f28994a173f15c5b9d970f7a692","tid":1736202,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b917d962